<h2>Email Change Request</h2>
<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>You requested to change your email address. To confirm this is you, please verify your current email:</p>

<div class="code-box">
  <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 10px;">Your Verification Code:</div>
  <div class="code">{{verificationCode}}</div>
</div>

<div class="warning">
  <ul>
    <li>This code expires in <strong>10 minutes</strong></li>
    <li>Never share this code with anyone</li>
    <li>If you didn't request this change, someone may be trying to access your account</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>After verification, you'll be able to enter your new email address.</p>